Can't add a COVID test in 2.2.0 When adding a new test, where you're waiting for the result, the form gives an error message because an item is incomplete. After a bit of fiddling about I found that there is a hidden field on the form. This appears when the test has a positive or negative result, but is hidden if "awaiting results". A workaround is to select "negative" on the result, answer "no" to the question about rapid testing, and then go back and select "awaiting results".
